com.siperian.sif.message.hm

Class SearchHmQueryResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianResponse
      • com.siperian.sif.message.mrm.SearchResponseBase
        • com.siperian.sif.message.hm.SearchHmQueryResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataProvider, RecordsProvider, Serializable

    public class SearchHmQueryResponse
extends SearchResponseBase
    This is a response for the SearchHmQueryRequest. It contains the list of Record objects. The SiperianObjectUid for the Records returned is the same as the SiperianObjectUid set in the SearchHmQueryRequest (that is, it will be either like HM_ENTITY_TYPE.xxx or HM_RELATIONSHIP_TYPE.yyy). The response may also contain the count of the total number of records that matched the query and a search token that can be used to fetch subsequent pages using GetSearchResultsRequest.

    See SearchHmQueryRequest for a description of this request.

    See Also:
    SearchHmQueryRequest, GetSearchResultsRequest, SearchResponseBase, SiperianResponse, Serialized Form

    API Pair: SearchHmQueryRequest

    API Group: Data Retrieval
